The paper deals with image-caption retrieval, which is a task related to computer vision (CV) and natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, cs.CV and cs.CL are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also discusses the use of uncertainty measures in deep learning, which falls under the category of machine learning (ML). Hence, cs.LG is also a likely sub-category. The paper also involves similarity functions, which is a topic related to information retrieval (IR) and multimedia (MM). Therefore, cs.IR and cs.MM are also possible sub-categories.
